A WellForge full-stack monorepo: Spring Boot 4 Kotlin backend + React TypeScript Vite frontend.

## Quickstart

```bash
# One-time: install the Maven plugin for mise
mise plugin install maven https://github.com/mise-plugins/mise-maven

mise trust          # trust this repo's mise.toml (once)
mise install        # install pinned tools (Java, Node, Maven, pnpm)
mise run install    # resolve backend + frontend dependencies
mise run dev        # start backend + frontend
```

## Layout

| Path | Contents |
|---|---|
| `backend/` | Spring Boot 4 + Kotlin service (jOOQ, Liquibase, Spring Modulith) |
| `frontend/` | React + TypeScript + Vite app (Mantine, TanStack, Effect TS) |
| `specs/` | Spec-driven feature work (see `specs/README.md`) |
| `mise.toml` | Pinned tools + root aggregate tasks |
{% if db == 'postgres' %}| `docker-compose.yml` | Local PostgreSQL for the backend |
{% endif %}| `AGENTS.md` | Project context for AI agents (CLAUDE.md imports it for Claude Code) |

## Commands

| Command | Action |
|---|---|
| `mise run install` | Install all dependencies |
| `mise run build` | Build backend + frontend |
| `mise run test` | Run all tests |
| `mise run lint` | Lint all services |
| `mise run dev` | Start everything in dev mode |

Single-service tasks: `mise run backend:<task>` / `mise run frontend:<task>`.

See [AGENTS.md](./AGENTS.md) for the full stack reference and conventions.
